name: Something Exquisite No.17
description: From ‘Something Exquisite in Monochromatic Computerized Abstraction’. A series of 21 digital artworks. In this work AJ processing 1027 thematic photographs into StyleGAN Model to extend the original body of work by presenting the genealogy of image forming process. The images are deconstructed and linkage with each other & the ‘in between’ quality seems appeared to emphasize the cohesive conception value that brings by the artworks. •1024px1024p •Mp4-25fps •ComputerArt •StyleGan •Audio by ob1K
